The paper discusses information assurance and access control in online universities, which are common topics in the computer security (cs.CR) and cyber security (cs.CY) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the implementation of identity and access management systems, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. Additionally, the construction and maintenance of the infrastructure is discussed, which could be categorized under the computer communications (cs.CC) and programming languages (cs.PL) sub-categories.
